579
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:28,760
What happened?

580
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:33,600
They took us out.

581
00:42:33,600 --> 00:42:40,000
In the night. In the dark.

582
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:42,200
