going to a new home.

584
00:42:46,200 --> 00:42:48,360
Who did, who said?

585
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:52,560
The staff. A care home?

586
00:42:56,400 --> 00:42:59,360
They drove us
away for miles and miles.

587
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:01,960
HIGH-PITCHED GIGGLING

588
00:43:04,720 --> 00:43:06,960
They were there.

589
00:43:06,960 --> 00:43:08,880
In the sky. What did they look like?

590
00:43:11,120 --> 00:43:12,560
Light.

591
00:43:19,120 --> 00:43:20,880
The light...

592
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:24,960
