593
00:43:26,760 --> 00:43:29,840
Took who? My friends. But not you?

594
00:43:33,520 --> 00:43:36,280
I ran.

595
00:43:39,480 --> 00:43:42,160
There was something,
there was people, there was..

596
00:43:42,800 --> 00:43:45,960
Isn't it, isn't it,
isn't it, isn't it?

597
00:43:48,160 --> 00:43:50,440
You're all right,

598
00:43:50,440 --> 00:43:51,960
