00:43:51,960 --> 00:43:53,360
You're safe now.

600
00:43:53,360 --> 00:43:56,120
But they're coming back.

601
00:43:58,160 --> 00:44:01,000
I've been smelling them for months.

602
00:44:03,320 --> 00:44:05,040
In the air.

603
