624
00:45:27,960 --> 00:45:30,680
Everything all right?
Yes. I'm fine, thank you.

625
00:45:30,680 --> 00:45:33,080
Right, well,
I think you've had long enough.

626
00:45:33,080 --> 00:45:36,120
Time for your meds, isn't it, Tim?
